## Summary

| # | Severity | Category | Finding |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | HIGH | Missing Done Criteria | E3 test uses `input[type=range]` — actual DOM has `input[type=number]` → test gate fails |
| 2 | MEDIUM | Edge Case + Missing Done Criteria | No-grid-cover no-lead case: TitleBlock marginBottom gap lost, undocumented invariant |
| 3 | MEDIUM | Missing Done Criteria | LayoutEditor.tsx stale-mode dead code not in Files-to-Change — Codex P2 finding likely |
| 4 | LOW | Ambiguity | parseImageCount cleanup left as implementer judgment — should be definitive |

**Verdict: NEEDS WORK**

Findings 1–3 must be addressed before implementation. Finding 4 is a strong recommendation. No finding requires a SPLIT.
